                <note rend="inline" type="source">361.11/3724: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Norway</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Schmedeman</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Christiania</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-05-12T15:00:00+01:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 12, 1921—3 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received May 12—2:39 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>19. Your 19, May 10, noon. Nansen much pleased with your message and sees no
                    objection to publication. He thinks of sending the text to the Soviets.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Schmedeman</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
